text: The Division of Fenner is an Australian electoral division in the Australian Capital Territory (ACT). It also includes the Jervis Bay Territory (JBT). It was created in 2016, replacing the Fraser (which was relocated to Melbourne). ==Members== Image Member Party Term Andrew Leigh Labor 2019-present ==Election results== ==References== Category:Electoral divisions of the Australian Capital Territory Category:2019 establishments in Australia
